away his wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=24'>Ezr 10:24</a><br/> 12. A son of Bani, who put away his wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=42'>Ezr 10:42</a><br/> 13. A Jew who repaired a portion of the wall of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=12'>Neh 3:12</a><br/> 14. Uncle of Jeremiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=7'>Jer 32:7</a><br/> 15. Father of Maaseiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=35&verse=4'>Jer 35:4</a>"}]}